/web.archive.org/web/20160413234643/http://www.hkgolden.com/</a><br />\n2016年4月13號 晚上11點46分 今天貼文總數: 1,619 <br />\n<br />\n分左家 做大個餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27f90bc2bdfe30710ffc5b372beac743adcd1d2","tid":502873,"uid":24282,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但連登都未達到分家前全盛時期(翻睇資料大約都係每日千幾個貼文(即係post)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20160413234643/http://www.hkgolden.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20160413234643%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2F&d=z4J2ajRam%2B%2F7icYaYlpPXLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=aeeed7d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://web.archive.org/web/20160413234643/http://www.hkgolden.com/</a><br />\n2016年4月13號 晚上11點46分 今天貼文總數: 1,619 <br />\n<br />\n分左家 做大個餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高登個貼文總數好鬼架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/185704_982f8df8896202b9acef767bf466e22e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F185704_982f8df8896202b9acef767bf466e22e.jpg&h=fa9eb991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Marshall Chan</strong><br />\n<br />\nhkg 條數咁鬼，當佢朝早4點幾當新一日計，幾分鐘內點樣有七百幾個新post? 而每日新post 條數同總post 數又點計都唔岩，睇唔透<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Gap撈Tech</strong>   Marshall Chan<br />\n<br />\n做之前留意咗幾日，發現今天貼文總數根本就係假嘅(唔知佢點定義）"},{"pid":"59c760cddc181052d46dcce90afc3f5e0c1e0589","tid":502873,"uid":1556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"原來仲要係做假數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3e718824129cf7d18aeab83f